12
00:00:46,544 --> 00:00:47,274
What?

13
00:00:51,014 --> 00:00:52,194
Sorry...

14
00:00:52,754 --> 00:00:53,924
I'm sorry, ma'am.

15
00:00:55,904 --> 00:00:57,994
These kids are cursing me to death!

16
00:01:14,374 --> 00:01:15,264
Boon.

17
00:01:21,404 --> 00:01:22,224
Boon...

18
00:01:33,614 --> 00:01:34,544
Why are we stopping?

19
00:01:35,464 --> 00:01:36,694
You're hungry.

20
00:01:36,734 --> 00:01:38,124
I can hear your stomach growling.

21
00:01:39,144 --> 00:01:40,274
What do you wanna eat?

22
00:01:40,854 --> 00:01:41,854
How about...

23
00:01:44,574 --> 00:01:45,794
rice and curry?

24
00:01:47,194 --> 00:01:48,474
7 days from now,

25
00:01:48,814 --> 00:01:51,444
